description:
Go behind the scenes of the Peacemaker Season 1 finale ‘It’s Cow or Never’ with James Gunn, Jennifer Holland (Emilia Harcourt) & Steve Agee (John Economos) in the official Peacemaker podcast. Hear exclusive stories about the shocking Justice League cameo, Peacemaker’s toughest choices, and the powerful ending that defined the HBO Max hit. Discover the rewarding pay-off of John Economos’ dye-beard monologue, find out who was the worst dancer in the now-iconic opening credits, and get the inside scoop on character arcs and Season 2 teases. Stream Peacemaker on HBO Max and follow the podcast for more DC Universe insights. Don’t forget to join us for the Official Peacemaker Season 2 Companion Podcast - new episodes drop Thursdays right after each episode airs. Stream Peacemaker on HBO Max.
